                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860531-45-off251 t17860531-45-cd252"></join> last, four bushels of coals, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17860531-45-victim582" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Howard and <rs id="t17860531-45-viclabel253" type="occupation">Co.</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860531-45-victim582 t17860531-45-viclabel253"></join>
